        <dc:creator><![CDATA[kasper]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>Hi,</p>
<p>I released a slight change to the Frontity Contact Form 7 package now. I noticed that if you had the plugin Akismet active on your wp site, a script is added to forms that would fail, and the page with the form would fail to render. So I made a small change to ensure that the Akismet plugin can be active and do its job.</p>
